{"tid":1115393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[中國社會信用評分系統] 有無人覺得政府想借安心單野,想取得的士內鏡頭片段既擁有權?","createTime":"2019-04-19T06:51:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T18:35:51.000Z","uid":88743,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e717bfd43f287235c984d6ce27d59e918acb2dd3","tid":1115393,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:51:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/programmes/closerlook/5cb8b42ce60383800fecb192\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fprogrammes%2Fcloserlook%2F5cb8b42ce60383800fecb192&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSbktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=e5a78e73\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/programmes/closerlook/5cb8b42ce60383800fecb192</a><br />\n睇無線新聞 成十幾分鐘既專輯 就知輿論機器已全面啟動<br />\n<br />\n簡單D黎講 以安全理由<br />\n叫的士安裝鏡頭<br />\n相信的士司機為左保障自己一定會照做<br />\n最後再以私隱權為名<br />\n修例得所有的士鏡頭片段既擁有權<br />\n可能連巴士小巴都會受影響<br />\n<br />\n當政府權有鏡頭同片段既擁有權<br />\n佢時可以改做用ip cam去錄影 data直接飛去政府部門<br />\n<br />\n而家公廁又話加鏡頭<br />\n又周圍都係天眼<br />\n中國社會信用評分系統就黎係香港適用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知中國社會信用評分系統係乜 可以google下 同睇下台灣新聞點解釋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WRPAe6xLzp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWRPAe6xLzp8&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSbktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=1880dc78\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WRPAe6xLzp8</a><br />\n<br />\n我就唔驚既 行得正企得正驚佢乜野中國社會信用評分系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb214002bfac4f3e7b27deed7f8788890b94fb2e","tid":1115393,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:55:20.000Z","msg":"正經post無人理?<br />\n定係連登己經唔討論得國情?"},{"pid":"38e7d7cb66883073b68c152f29273260ade21cb9","tid":1115393,"